      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastic-plastic constitutive model with isotropic hardening justified by material characterization data; contact formulation validated against coupon-level tests.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model for Ti-6Al-4V screw and cobalt-chrome rod validated against uniaxial tensile coupon data. Augmented Lagrange contact at screw-rod interface captures load transfer mechanism consistent with observed experimental failure modes."
