      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific tensile testing of production material; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of tested specimens; friction coefficient from dedicated tribology study.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength sourced from manufacturer certificate of conformance averages rather than lot-specific tensile coupon testing of the actual test specimens. Friction coefficient adopted from published literature (0.2) without dedicated tribology characterization for this specific screw-rod material pairing. Geometric inputs are from nominal CAD rather than CMM measurements of the 11 tested constructs. These input uncertainties are acknowledged but not fully propagated into the validation metric, meaning the achieved level of 2 falls short of the required level of 3 for this factor."
    },
