      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span the range of COU loading scenarios including at least two rod diameters and two load levels; environmental conditions (temperature, humidity) monitored and reported.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (compression-bending at standard crosshead displacement rate). No variation in rod diameter, load angle, or displacement rate was explored. Environmental conditions (ambient laboratory, 23°C) are representative but only one test condition was evaluated, which is insufficient to characterize the model's predictive capability across the COU design space. Achieved level 2 is below the required level 3."
    },
