      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm (1.04). All three QoIs pass the pre-specified acceptance threshold of 1.96. Uncertainty budget separates simulation numerical uncertainty, model parameter uncertainty, and experimental measurement uncertainty. Validation metric methodology consistent with ASME V&V 40 Section 5."
    },
